---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Slots Math Guide">
  <div class="pt-36 pb-10">
    <div class="w-full h-full mx-auto px-5 max-w-screen-md">
      <div class="animate">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 dark:border-white/20 bg-white/70 dark:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur p-7 md:p-10">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-black/60 dark:text-white/60">Ontario-first • Math-first • Terms-first</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-black dark:text-white mt-3">Slots, bonuses, and withdrawals, explained with clarity.</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">Premium plain-English guides to RTP, volatility, wagering requirements, and withdrawal timelines. No hype, no promises, just understanding.</p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="/slot-guides/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-black text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-black font-semibold">Start with Guides</a>
            <a href="/casino-bonuses/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-black/15 dark:border-white/25 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 font-semibold">Bonuses</a>
            <a href="/payments-and-withdrawals/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-black/15 dark:border-white/25 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 font-semibold">Withdrawals</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mt-6">
          <a class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 dark:border-white/20 bg-white/70 dark:bg-white/5 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" href="/rtp-in-slots/">
            <div class="text-sm uppercase text-black/60 dark:text-white/60">Start here</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">RTP in Slots</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">What RTP means, what it doesn’t, and how to interpret it safely.</div>
          </a>
          <a class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 dark:border-white/20 bg-white/70 dark:bg-white/5 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" href="/wagering-requirements/">
            <div class="text-sm uppercase text-black/60 dark:text-white/60">Most searched</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Wagering Requirements</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">How playthrough works, with simple examples and pitfalls.</div>
          </a>
          <a class="p-5 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 dark:border-white/20 bg-white/70 dark:bg-white/5 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10" href="/withdrawal-times/">
            <div class="text-sm uppercase text-black/60 dark:text-white/60">Practical</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Withdrawal Times</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">Processing vs delivery time, common delays, and what to do next.</div>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-black/10 dark:border-white/20 bg-white/70 dark:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur p-7 md:p-10 mt-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Affiliate partners</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-black/70 dark:text-white/70">We’re preparing a curated, terms-first directory. If you’re an operator or network partner, contact us to be included.</p>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <a href="/contact/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-black/15 dark:border-white/25 hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 font-semibold">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
